description: Nearly 1,000 more voters register than for the 2016 general election, the highest since 2008.
title: More than 31,000 registered on Guernsey electoral roll
title_page: More than 31,000 registered on Guernsey electoral roll - BBC News
maintext: This is nearly 1,000 more people than were on the roll at the 2016 election and the most since 2008, the States of Guernsey said.
